Thanks to all other language moderators!

249
00:20:50,237 --> 00:20:54,185
Wait, hold on a second.

250
00:20:56,031 --> 00:20:58,808
That wasn't funny.

251
00:20:58,808 --> 00:21:02,181
Nozue-san, you're almost in your forties.

252
00:21:02,181 --> 00:21:04,607
Be more careful about where you confess your love.

253
00:21:04,607 --> 00:21:08,589
You're in your thirties, so be more careful where you take me.

254
00:21:11,422 --> 00:21:13,816
- Nozue-san.
- Yeah?

255
00:21:15,128 --> 00:21:17,019
It's okay.

256
00:21:17,967 --> 00:21:21,160
Having an age gap or being a minority

257
00:21:21,160 --> 00:21:24,859
is the same as having different hometowns

258
00:21:24,859 --> 00:21:29,579
or cheering for a different baseball team.

259
00:21:29,579 --> 00:21:31,656
It's nothing.

260
00:21:34,738 --> 00:21:40,329
Let's have more fights, disagreements, and misunderstandings.

261
00:21:41,226 --> 00:21:46,887
And let's keep making up like this all the way until our eighties.

262
00:21:48,705 --> 00:21:52,210
What about when we're 81?

263
00:21:59,599 --> 00:22:02,864
I'll go get my bag.

264
00:22:03,869 --> 00:22:05,605
Please stay here.

265
00:22:05,605 --> 00:22:07,308
Sure.

266
00:22:08,696 --> 00:22:10,475
Don't leave, okay?

267
00:22:10,475 --> 00:22:12,281
I got it.

268
00:22:12,281 --> 00:22:15,538
Don't move from here.

269
00:22:15,538 --> 00:22:19,003
Come on, hurry and go get it.

270
00:22:22,256 --> 00:22:25,969
I'm almost 40, but I feel like I might kiss you anywhere.

271
00:22:32,008 --> 00:22:34,009
Darn it.

272
00:22:47,402 --> 00:22:49,303
I got this confirmed.

273
00:22:49,303 --> 00:22:51,740
Thank you.

274
00:22:55,911 --> 00:22:59,340
Hey, Takase-kun.

275
00:23:01,513 --> 00:23:03,882
Make the font big, as usual.

276
00:23:03,882 --> 00:23:05,482
Okay.

277
00:23:13,044 --> 00:23:16,056
Hey, let's go to lunch.

278
00:23:16,056 --> 00:23:20,444
Sure, let's go with Togawa.

279
00:23:20,444 --> 00:23:22,585
